title: Top 10 Songs of Lopamudra Mitra | Bengali Hit Songs | Audio Jukebox
description:
Jukebox presents 10 SMASH HITS Modern songs rendered by Lopamudra Mitra. These songs are compiled from her various music  albums for your listening pleasure. 2nd, 4th & 10th songs are vocally supported by the Band artistes of AGANTUK. Hope you will like this selection of songs. So, Please listen, Enjoy & Share these.
